  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tTransform<br />\n\tTo transform is to change to a different state. What is transforming? Why is it doing so? What was it like before the transformation? What is the outcome?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They transformed... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) vehicles transforming into robots<br />\n\t2) a piece of clothing can be transformed into various styles to suit to occasion<br />\n\t3) reading a book and changing one's life<br />\n\t4) magic tricks of transforming one object into another<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t&ldquo;Welcome to our establishment,&rdquo; the club manager said as he extended a hand to the arriving <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/corporate\" target=\"_blank\">corporate</a> clients. The setup for the launch event was almost completed; staffs were finishing up with last minute touches. Working with the party planner, the club manager <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/oversee\" target=\"_blank\">oversaw</a> everything down to the minute details. The club had be transformed completely to suit the brand image of the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/cologne\" target=\"_blank\">cologne</a> being launched. As they toured around the venue, the club manager highlighted the details to the corporate clients, who seemed impressed with the layout and d&eacute;cor, especially the attention to details.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/162531631417/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p727374/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p727374\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p728709/\">超法国！ 中国成为世界第二大酿酒葡萄产地</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p729093/\">《权力的游戏》精讲 \"看\"的多样英文表达</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p729303/\">凯特王妃顺利诞下女婴 英国王室喜添新成员</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p728914/\">穿裙子的男人 英国传统服饰知多少？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p728958/\">低头党威力大 2016中国手游市场全球第一</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p728950/\">测一测：你是哪种类型的吃货？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p728760/\">流利英文 别让how are you毁了第一印象</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p532552/\">免费在线学：CCTalk英语大厅课程表</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p728594/\">组图：世界最叹为观止的八大奇景</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p1